    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-05-24T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-05-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="599"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d599">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Germany</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_GJW1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gerard</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-05-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 24, 1915</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Answering your 2277, May 22, 12 m., have asked <persName corresp="#p_DCT1"
                        >Dumba</persName> to call at 4 p. m. Will secure from him and cable you a
                    statement denying the reported communication to <persName corresp="#p_ZAFM1"
                        >Zimmermann</persName>, or correcting the construction placed upon it. I
                    need not tell you that there is absolutely no justification for his report and
                    you will please so notify the Government at once. The Government must not, for a
                    moment, misunderstand the language or intent of the note regarding the submarine
                    attack on the <hi rend="italic">Lusitania, Gulflight, Gushing</hi>, and <hi
                        rend="italic">Falaba</hi>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_BWJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
